    format("MAY: {PLAYER}{KUN}!\p I was just checking my POKéDEX.\p There's still a lot of POKéMON that I've seen but haven't caught.\p And there are many others that I think will evolve.\p I wonder where I should go catch some POKéMON next?")
}

